{
  "stem": "2833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then on top of it, we got a typhoid, typhoid epidemic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you know, this was an hour and a half away from Prague and in the middle of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the Germans got terribly scared of epidemics anyways.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had marvelous doctors who had come from Prague and Brunn and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't have medication, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't have enough to treat them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when that typhoid epidemic came, then all of a sudden, you know, we got what we needed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was really contained and taken care of in, in a marvelous way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in that one hospital, they had a park around the building.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, they had put some cots that people who were like me had to lie there during the day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't want us to-- you know, other people to catch whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while that-- while we were there, they made that famous film where the, the Fuhrer gave a city to the Jews, it was called.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was made for the Swedish Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I, I worked a little bit on it, too, because we had-- they build a merry-go-round.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to find children, because I worked also in the, in the-- taking care of the kitchen of the children's home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And these children had to be trained that they go on the merry-go-round and that the SS man is going to stand there and hand each of the child when it goes by a box of sardines.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were supposed to say, again, sardines, Uncle Rahm-- was his name, at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on the other end of it, I stood and took them away from them because the whole thing was a sham.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
